{"tid":2336978,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港聞專題：逾千小店合辦黃色聖誕周  吃喝玩樂 缺一不可","createTime":"2020-12-23T04:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T14:28:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7ddda8e26eb6b8c4818ad14444eb9082a312dc47","tid":2336978,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:14:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/F6LOGMHNEFBAXDZL2JWIMIEF3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2FF6LOGMHNEFBAXDZL2JWIMIEF3E%2F&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpPPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=6b4e006d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2FF6LOGMHNEFBAXDZL2JWIMIEF3E%2F&h=09bec72c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/F6LOGMHNEFBAXDZL2JWIMIEF3E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港聞專題：逾千小店合辦黃色聖誕周 <br />\n吃喝玩樂 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p8YXd-N3bDq-6fkdTwMMr7QCNqY=/1181x809/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3RL27ZLY65BF7BTXYK3ECDGLN4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp8YXd-N3bDq-6fkdTwMMr7QCNqY%3D%2F1181x809%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3RL27ZLY65BF7BTXYK3ECDGLN4.jpg&h=89e92755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「聖誕課金週」由本月19日至27日舉行，當中分為「扮靚週」、「狂歡週」和「美食週」。<br />\n<br />\n去年香港過了一個黑色聖誕，不明身份的蒙面人員四出開槍圍捕；。。。。。。。。。。。。。外賣大餐、12人到會&hellip;&hellip;一年半過去，香港人夢未完。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：早備餐單等12人回港<br />\n記者：張文鈴<br />\n<br />\n攝影：謝榮耀 王子俊 王瑋彤<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：五食肆首創聯合到會<br />\n<br />\n臨近聖誕佳節，雙拾團隊月中起推出「聖誕課金週」，當中分為「扮靚週」、「狂歡週」和「美食週」。活動贊助商「夠薑媒體」項目總監Vivian說，舉辦活動是希望提醒港人繼續支持香港本地良心店，「因為疫情關係，呢一年小店真係好難捱」。<br />\n<br />\n政府本月起收緊防疫措施，限聚令回復至兩人後，生意更加慘淡，且晚上6時後禁堂食，令食肆影響更大，「見到有啲情況係做串燒，淨係做晚市，變咗要研究埋賣晏晝飯盒⋯⋯大家都諗盡辦法做生意，做得幾多得幾多」。<br />\n<br />\n「聖誕課金週」有逾1,100間黃店參加，當中22%食肆、26%零售、22%服務類、30%其他。Vivian說，原先目標是參考11月底同類活動有2,000間黃店參與，但認為今次活動宣傳不足，且相信參與黃店數量與疫情很大關係，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JbhyBtU8AMtsOAdRPKoByHw7RzY=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FWQF7FPNKRBMNL7RNTYEW4UDWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJbhyBtU8AMtsOAdRPKoByHw7RzY%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFWQF7FPNKRBMNL7RNTYEW4UDWE.jpg&h=1e7c79ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Vivian舉辦此活動是希望港人繼續支持本地良心店。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nAGp7gJdWx2G63lfkZLcKmuzvBg=/1181x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2I7GBQ2DZNC6BLSVTGZA5Y6QPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnAGp7gJdWx2G63lfkZLcKmuzvBg%3D%2F1181x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2I7GBQ2DZNC6BLSVTGZA5Y6QPE.jpg&h=ba2e0217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「夠薑媒體」推出的「人鏈利是封」一套20個，備有黃色及灰色選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推「人鏈利是封」<br />\n<br />\n「夠薑媒體」特別設計六款Postcard，消費者只要光顧四類指定的黃店就有機會儲齊一套，「大家習慣咗去食肆消費，但忽略咗其他行業都需要支持，所以呢個Postcard Game想呼籲大家關注各行各業」。「夠薑媒體」亦提早推出「人鏈利是封」，一套20個，利是封圖案可拼成一幅人鏈圖。<br />\n<br />\n本港經濟受疫情嚴重影響，年尾有公司宣佈裁員，甚至倒閉。港人消費力將較往。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有商戶向她反映更擔心執法者選擇性執法，「總之你（黃店）做生意，（執法者）執法好嚴謹，反而對（其他）唔同色彩嘅舖頭會鬆手啲，（黃店）係揸得咁正嘅情況底下好難做落去」。<br />\n<br />\n上月底有民間舉辦黃色經濟圈活動「傘心市集」，但活動疑遭打壓腰斬。Vivian說：「（課金週）唔排除有呢啲情況發生，但我哋只能夠見步行步，做得幾多得幾多（有冇對策？）暫時未傾到」。傘心市集受到打壓，「接落嚟我哋自己呢邊有唔同市集，但因為限聚令陸陸續續取消，大家對12月、甚至去到新年情況，咁啲市集可能有機會都係取消」，料未來打壓將越來越多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bzVOOtPPx4o1KCfV220JFb1SUNs=/2358x3801/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AGKNJLHHVNEZLOOD4AOR4DTOOQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbzVOOtPPx4o1KCfV220JFb1SUNs%3D%2F2358x3801%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAGKNJLHHVNEZLOOD4AOR4DTOOQ.jpg&h=70bf5a70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d6aee300309028b1a38f156ebfab530a5ea4d08","tid":2336978,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:17:01.000Z","msg":"想買利是封<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e449809c6f439873d7a36e4a6a799d858d8c2bb","tid":2336978,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"好開心又到黃色消費週！"},{"pid":"f6f1daa81493c209b42a56decb74de111a96d5f5","tid":2336978,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005e6b5c00bfa05a8c7022e2193f4b2aba812108","tid":2336978,"uid":33668,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:21:35.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢吃喝玩樂 缺一不可<br />\n蘋果可唔可以有D政治智慧"},{"pid":"d87ecc5a6d6c12afc7c7a325f5ad36d00524f19b","tid":2336978,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GQJ2Yqq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGQJ2Yqq.jpg&h=cda7414b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ca5ff4933a75268bf44b57b2a0bc92a483f9cc9","tid":2336978,"uid":88134,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"005e6b5c00bfa05a8c7022e2193f4b2aba812108","tid":2336978,"uid":33668,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:21:35.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢吃喝玩樂 缺一不可<br />\n蘋果可唔可以有D政治智慧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:57:33.000Z","msg":"佢啲讀者都弱智既，咁佢又洗乜有智慧？"},{"pid":"498086555